in a career of 897 games , krushelnyski recorded 241 goals and 328 assists for 569 career points ; his single best season was 1984 - 85 , in which he scored 43 goals and 88 points while often playing as a winger on a line with gretzky and jari kurri .

1988 : this edmonton oiler was traded to the l.a. kings with mike krushelnyski & marty mcsorley

